compiler/backend/bytecode_gen/verifier.runa
Bytecode Verification and Validation System

This module provides comprehensive bytecode verification functionality including:
- Bytecode structural integrity verification
- Type safety validation and checking
- Control flow consistency verification
- Stack depth and balance validation
- Exception handling correctness verification
- Memory access bounds checking
- Function signature and calling convention validation
- Profiling metadata consistency checking
- Deoptimization metadata validation
- Speculation point consistency verification
- AOTT metadata integrity checking
- Cross-module reference validation
- Security constraint enforcement
- Runtime safety property verification
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

